attributes.Long form description: The student flips the table over and begins to unscrew the top corners of the table. Next, the student unscrews the legs one by one from the shelf. Finally, the student separates the shelf.

attributes.Action sentence: The student unscrews the first corner of the table.
The student unscrews the second corner of the table.
The student unscrews the third corner of the table.
The student disassembles the first leg of the shelf.
The student disassembles the second leg from the shelf.
The student disassembles the third leg from the shelf.
The student disassembles the last leg from the shelf.
